webpackJsonp([24825738488748],{7394:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{post:{html:'<p>My wife\'s company has been sponsoring the <a href="http://www.hsv.de/">local soccer team</a> for I don\'t know how many years now, and today for the first time she brought home match tickets. But somehow I don\'t think the tickets are very good. </p>\n<p>For one thing, the match is against <a href="http://www.fcbayern.t-com.de/de/index.php" title="FC Bayern M&uuml;nchen">Bayern M&uuml;nchen</a>, a team they haven\'t beaten in years and a match they are sure to lose. </p>\n<p>And for another thing, the <a href="http://www.hsv.de/index.php?id=8817" title="Hamburger SV: Business-Seats West">seats are behind glass</a> and pretty far from the playing field. I\'m sure we won\'t be able to <a href="http://www.hsv.de/index.php?id=12814">see or hear well</a> at all.</p>\n<p>Well, the tickets didn\'t cost us anything, so I guess we should be happy that we\'ll be going to a game at all. At least they are for a league match and not for some <a href="http://fifaworldcup.yahoo.com/06/en/">meaningless international tournament</a>.</p>',fields:{title:"Bad Tickets",date:"09 Aug 2005",url:"https://papascott.de/2005-08-09-bad-tickets/"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/2005-08-09-bad-tickets/",prev:{fields:{title:"Half Empty or Half Dead?",date:"07 Aug 2005",slug:"/2005-08-07-half-empty-or-half-dead/"}},next:{fields:{title:"Moving Blog",date:"10 Aug 2005",slug:"/2005-08-10-moving-blog/"}}}}}});
//# sourceMappingURL=path---2005-08-09-bad-tickets-3de8c00daaf7316519d0.js.map